<body>

<div class="container">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">

      <!-- blog entry -->
      <h1 style="color:navy;">Welcome!</a>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead">City of Houston Campaign Finance Application Module</a>
      </p>
      <hr>
      <img src="http://placehold.it/900x300" class="img-responsive">
      <hr>
      <p>This is a very basic starter template for a blog homepage. It makes use of Glyphicons that are built into Bootstrap 3, and it makes use of the Pager at the bottom of the page. Make sure you get the Glyphicons files by downloading the entire
        <code>/fonts</code>directory that you can download in the source files or at <a href="http://getbootstrap.com">getbootstrap.com</a>. That directory has all of the web fonts in it which makes Glyphicons work.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Read More <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>

      <hr>


    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">

      <!-- /well -->
      <div class="well">
        <h4 style="color:darkgreen;">Campaign Finance Navigation</h4>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10">
            <ul class="list-center">
              <li><%= link_to "Home", loginhome_path %></a>
              </li>
              <li><%= link_to "New Report", new_campaign_finance_info_path %></a>
              </li>
              <li><%= link_to "My Reports", campaign_finance_infos_path %></a>
              </li>
              <li><%= link_to "Instructions", campaign_finance_infos_path %></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="well">
        <h4 style="color:darkgreen;">Registration</h4>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10">
            <ul class="list-center">
              <li><%= link_to "Register Candidate", new_candidate_path %></a>
              </li>
              <li><%= link_to "Register Treasurer", new_treasurer_path %></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="well">
        <h4 style="color:darkgreen;">City of Houston Links</h4>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10">
            <ul class="list-center">
              <li><a href="http://www.houstontx.gov/">City of Houston</a>
              </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.houstontx.gov/council/">City Council</a>
              </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.houstontx.gov/redirect/harriscountyclerk.html">County Clerk</a>
              </li>
              <li><a href="http://www.houstontx.gov/citysec/">City Secretary</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- /well -->
      <div class="well">
        <h4 style="color:red;">DISCLAIMER</h4>
        <p>Electronic data entered into this system will be subject to Texas Public Information Act requests. Disclosure of the information will be required unless exempted under a specific provision of the Act.</br>
          <br>The law requires that data entered into this system be readily available to the public within two (2) business days.</br>
          Enter only data required by Title 15 of the Texas Election Code, and Chapter 18 of the Code of Ordinances, Houston TX.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- /well -->
    </div>
